OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779753774
OL,3,CAt least 23 killed and 70 wounded
OL,4,Cafter bomb attack near train in
OL,5,CPakistan
OL,7,FAt least 23 people have been killed
OL,8,Fand 70 wounded after a suicide bomber
OL,9,Fdetonated an explosives-laden vehicle
OL,10,Fnear a railway track as a passenger
OL,11,Ftrain passed in Pakistan.
OL,13,FThe attack happened in the
OL,14,Fsouthwestern city of Quetta on Sunday.
OL,16,FThe force of the blast caused two
OL,17,Ftrain carriages to overturn and catch
OL,18,Ffire, sending thick black smoke into
OL,19,Fthe air, according to footage shared
OL,20,Fonline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
