PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779753774
OL,3,CAt least 23 killed and 70 wounded
OL,4,Cafter bomb attack near train in
OL,5,CPakistan
OL,7,FThe blast hit an area where security
OL,8,Fforces are usually stationed, badly
OL,9,Fdamaging nearby buildings and wrecking
OL,10,Fmore than a dozen parked vehicles,
OL,11,Faccording to witnesses and images
OL,12,Fshared on social media.
OL,14,FDoctors at local hospitals said they
OL,15,Fhad received the wounded, with 20 in a
OL,16,Fcritical condition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
