PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779753774
OL,3,CAt least 23 killed and 70 wounded
OL,4,Cafter bomb attack near train in
OL,5,CPakistan
OL,7,FThe banned Baloch Liberation Army, or
OL,8,FBLA, which wants independence from
OL,9,FPakistan's central government, claimed
OL,10,Fresponsibility for the attack, saying
OL,11,Fit had targeted a train carrying
OL,12,Fsecurity personnel.
OL,14,FQuetta is the capital of Balochistan
OL,15,Fprovince, which has long been the
OL,16,Fscene of a low-level insurgency.
OL,18,FThe oil and mineral-rich region has
OL,19,Ffrequently seen attacks on security
OL,20,Fforces, government buildings and
OL,21,Fcivilians.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
