PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779753774
OL,3,CAt least 23 killed and 70 wounded
OL,4,Cafter bomb attack near train in
OL,5,CPakistan
OL,7,F"We strongly condemn the targeting of
OL,8,Finnocent civilians and are deeply
OL,9,Fsaddened by the loss of precious human
OL,10,Flives. Terrorist elements deserve no
OL,11,Fleniency," Shahid Rind, Balochistan
OL,12,Fprovincial government spokesman, said.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
