PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779753774
OL,3,CAt least 23 killed and 70 wounded
OL,4,Cafter bomb attack near train in
OL,5,CPakistan
OL,7,FHe said following the explosion, a
OL,8,Fmedical emergency was declared at
OL,9,Fhospitals in Quetta, and an
OL,10,Finvestigation has been launched.
OL,12,FPrime Minister Shehbaz Sharif strongly
OL,13,Fcondemned the attack, calling it a
OL,14,F"cowardly act of terrorism" in a post
OL,15,Fon X and offering condolences to the
OL,16,Ffamilies of the victims.
OL,18,FAlthough Pakistani authorities say
OL,19,Fthey have quelled the insurgency,
OL,20,Fviolence in Baluchistan has persisted.
